### 健康检查
GET http://localhost:8081/api/health

### 查询统计看板
GET http://localhost:8081/api/dashboard

### 查询全部网络设备
GET http://localhost:8081/api/devices

### 按状态查询网络设备
GET http://localhost:8081/api/devices?status=WARNING

### 新增网络设备
POST http://localhost:8081/api/devices
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "银川核心交换机备机",
  "assetCode": "SW-YC-CORE-02",
  "managementIp": "10.10.1.2",
  "deviceType": "Switch",
  "location": "银川政企机房",
  "status": "ONLINE",
  "ownerTeam": "网络运维组"
}

### 更新设备状态
PATCH http://localhost:8081/api/devices/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "MAINTENANCE"
}

### 查询全部告警
GET http://localhost:8081/api/alerts

### 按状态查询告警
GET http://localhost:8081/api/alerts?status=OPEN

### 新增告警
POST http://localhost:8081/api/alerts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceId": 1,
  "severity": "HIGH",
  "title": "链路丢包",
  "description": "上联链路出现丢包，需要检查端口和线路状态。",
  "source": "巡检"
}

### 更新告警状态
PATCH http://localhost:8081/api/alerts/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "PROCESSING",
  "handler": "曹博轩"
}

### 查询运维记录
GET http://localhost:8081/api/operation-records

### 导出设备台账 Excel
GET http://localhost:8081/api/devices/export

### 导入设备台账 Excel
POST http://localhost:8081/api/devices/import
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----NetworkAlertBoundary

------NetworkAlertBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample-network-devices-import.xlsx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet

< ./sample-network-devices-import.xlsx
------NetworkAlertBoundary--
